history.content:
Do upper-div courses that are crosslisted in Astro, Chem, Phys, Bio, etc... count towards the natural science elective requirement? And are there any lower-div courses we could take in these departments that aren't listed on the requirements page but would still be counted? (like EPS 80, MCB 55, etc)

Also, would classes in other science departments like Bioengineering count towards this requirement?
history.subject: Natural Science requirement
